# GeoScore project overview

GeoScore is a minimal SEO & GEO analyzer for websites and apps.

The product must feel as simple as a lightweight utility tool:
- paste URL
- click analyze
- get scores and fixes

But the analysis must be rigorous:
- deterministic rules first
- LLM second
- explainable scoring
- bounded cost
- visible confidence and limitations

## Product outputs

Every completed scan should return:
- global_score
- seo_score
- geo_score
- page_type_final
- analysis_confidence
- strengths
- issues
- recommendations
- limitations

## Product philosophy

Simple on the surface, serious underneath.

Do not bloat the product.
Do not design a full SEO suite.
Do not introduce hidden magic into scoring.

## Docs source of truth

The authoritative docs live in:
- docs/00-product/
